WEBVTT

00:00:56.059 --> 00:01:00.059
Specijalno za forum IPTV Zezanje

00:01:03.059 --> 00:01:05.059
<i>Taa li go napravi?</i>

00:01:06.332 --> 00:01:10.632
<i>Ne e li taa? Koj e vinoven?</i>

00:01:14.258 --> 00:01:16.258
<i>Bev sirak.</i>

00:01:16.689 --> 00:01:18.689
<i>Ŕmbrouz me zede.</i>

00:01:21.666 --> 00:01:23.666
<i>Ěi bese bratuced.</i>

00:01:24.425 --> 00:01:26.455
<i>No go sakav kako tatko.</i>

00:01:31.970 --> 00:01:34.140
<i>Rekoa deka na momceto mu treba majka,</i>

00:01:37.706 --> 00:01:41.156
<i>no edinstvenite dopusteni zenski
vo kucata, bea kucinjata.</i>

00:01:54.759 --> 00:01:57.489
<i>Se vrativ od uciliste.</i>
- Daj mi go toa.

00:02:03.459 --> 00:02:05.459
<i>Sto nauciv?</i>

00:02:08.627 --> 00:02:10.627
<i>Ne mi se dopadaa knigite.</i>

00:02:11.606 --> 00:02:13.606
<i>Ne gi sakav gradovite.</i>

00:02:14.891 --> 00:02:17.191
<i>Ne mi se dopadaa ni umnite razgovori.</i>

00:02:19.418 --> 00:02:22.718
<i>Ěi se dopadase ovde.</i>

00:02:29.648 --> 00:02:31.648
<i>No Ŕmbrouz se razbole.</i>

00:02:35.227 --> 00:02:37.237
<i>Lekarite go pratija</i>

00:02:38.362 --> 00:02:40.362
<i>na soncevo mesto.</i>

00:02:56.076 --> 00:02:58.076
<i>Kolku mi nedostasuva.</i>

00:03:01.033 --> 00:03:04.223
<i>Go spodeluvav sekoe pismo
so mojot kum i cerka mu.</i>

00:03:04.423 --> 00:03:07.315
Primiv pismo od Ŕmbrouz.
Tukusto pristigna.

00:03:07.491 --> 00:03:10.301
<i>No togas, ona leto,
vo negovite pisma se spomna...</i>

00:03:11.386 --> 00:03:15.176
<i>"Bratucetka mi,
isto i tvoja bratucetka,</i>

00:03:15.376 --> 00:03:18.171
<i>Rejcel, vdovica, cudesen sogovornik,</i>

00:03:18.371 --> 00:03:22.703
<i>koja ljubezno prifati da mi gi pokaze
site znamenitosti na Firenca.</i>

00:03:23.372 --> 00:03:27.042
<i>Taa zivee tuka na soncevo mesto,
no e anglicanka, kolku i ti..."</i>

00:03:27.335 --> 00:03:31.305
Sigurno e uzasno sarmantna,
za da ja zabelezi Ŕmbrouz.

00:03:31.505 --> 00:03:33.558
Sto sakas da kazes?

00:03:33.758 --> 00:03:36.095
Ne sum go cula da se vosőituva na zena.

00:03:36.335 --> 00:03:39.012
Prava e. Bratuced ti
nemase potreba od zeni.

00:03:39.324 --> 00:03:42.554
Zosto mu e? Ěe imase mene.

00:03:44.182 --> 00:03:47.682
Na kolku godini e?
- Ne pisuva.

00:03:48.889 --> 00:03:50.889
<i>Do esenta...</i>

00:03:51.479 --> 00:03:53.569
<i>Cudesni vesti.</i>

00:03:53.792 --> 00:03:55.792
<i>So Rejcel ce se vencame.</i>

00:03:56.350 --> 00:04:01.800
<i>Soglasna e.
Da e blagoslovena takva sreca.</i>

00:04:02.423 --> 00:04:05.653
<i>Siguren sum, deka vo momentot,
vo koj sto ce ja vidis ce razberes.</i>

00:04:06.628 --> 00:04:11.838
<i>Taa e sjajna,
dobra i najdobriot sogovornik."</i>

00:04:13.751 --> 00:04:17.162
Ke svrti se naopaku za sekunda.

00:04:20.799 --> 00:04:24.031
Nema da znaeme kade sme za sekunda.

00:04:27.755 --> 00:04:29.765
Si mislel li za idninata?

00:04:31.750 --> 00:04:33.824
Za svoj sopstven dom?

00:04:34.299 --> 00:04:36.649
Zosto po davolite treba da go pravam toa?

00:04:38.984 --> 00:04:41.340
Pomalku situacijata se menuva, neli?

00:04:48.504 --> 00:04:50.574
Koga gi ocekuvas?

00:04:50.774 --> 00:04:54.444
Bez somnenie, vo svojata sreca
zaboravil se za nas.

00:04:54.644 --> 00:04:57.230
Kutriot Filip, pak ce osiromasis.

00:04:57.758 --> 00:05:01.568
Smesen komentar.
- Óbavo e, sto e srecen, neli?

00:05:02.323 --> 00:05:04.393
Vo toa e celiot smisol, neli?

00:05:04.590 --> 00:05:07.681
Kakov smisol?
- Sto se zeni.

00:05:15.314 --> 00:05:17.531
Sigurna sum, deka brzo ce ima pismo.

00:05:21.918 --> 00:05:23.918
<i>"Ti pisav nekolku pati,</i>

00:05:24.658 --> 00:05:26.993
<i>no taa me posmatrase kako jastreb,</i>

00:05:28.187 --> 00:05:31.597
<i>a nema komu da se doveram
da mi gi odnese pismata vo postata.</i>

00:05:32.303 --> 00:05:34.393
<i>Denes ne e vo kucata.</i>

00:05:34.590 --> 00:05:36.590
<i>Ete zosto mozam da go napisam ova.</i>

00:05:39.765 --> 00:05:44.235
<i>So sedmici sum bolen.
Treski, uzasni glavobolki.</i>

00:05:44.423 --> 00:05:46.733
<i>Ěi se potkreva od gletkata na sonceto.</i>

00:05:47.070 --> 00:05:50.000
<i>Sto se odnesuva do lekarite,
ne veruvam nikomu od niv.</i>

00:05:50.155 --> 00:05:54.125
<i>Noviot, preporacan
od taa zmija, Renaldi,</i>

00:05:54.690 --> 00:05:56.690
<i>e ubiec, siguren sum."</i>

00:06:07.252 --> 00:06:09.252
Koj e Renaldi?

00:06:09.960 --> 00:06:12.590
Nemam pretstava.
- Ěoze li da poglednam?

00:06:18.899 --> 00:06:20.929
Pijan li bil, kako mislis?

00:06:21.410 --> 00:06:23.520
Pijan?
- Koga go napisal pismoto.

00:06:25.147 --> 00:06:27.147
Nikogas.

00:06:31.504 --> 00:06:33.504
Vidi.

00:06:33.740 --> 00:06:38.010
<i>"Najposle go napravi.
Rejcel, mojata tortura.</i>

00:06:39.080 --> 00:06:41.417
<i>Do Boga, ela brzo."</i>

00:06:45.618 --> 00:06:48.618
<i>BRŔTUCETKŔ ĚI REŁCEL</i>

00:07:47.384 --> 00:07:49.384
Ŕlo?

00:08:03.505 --> 00:08:05.505
Vie treba da ste Filip.

00:08:09.480 --> 00:08:11.480
Ve ocekuvav.

00:08:24.281 --> 00:08:26.291
Od kade znaete koj sum?

00:08:26.450 --> 00:08:30.300
Ne sum prviot, koj sto ja zabelezuva
prekrasnata prilika so bratuced vi.

00:08:30.460 --> 00:08:33.473
Ěolam, vlezete. Skoro zavrsiv.

00:08:36.787 --> 00:08:39.157
Kade e toj?
- Kade e toj?

00:08:39.565 --> 00:08:42.055
Sigurno, drag prijatele znaete...

00:08:46.001 --> 00:08:48.001
Toj e mrtov.

00:08:59.283 --> 00:09:01.283
Kade e zenata?

00:09:02.489 --> 00:09:06.379
Ćenata?
- Rejcel, kade e taa?

00:09:06.579 --> 00:09:08.594
Zamina.
- Kade?

00:09:08.794 --> 00:09:10.828
Nemam pretstava. Vistina e.

00:09:22.538 --> 00:09:24.538
Kako umre?

00:09:25.462 --> 00:09:29.112
Bese tumor vo glavata. Tuka.

00:09:29.279 --> 00:09:32.099
Lekarite ne se somnevaa,
deka mu go zafatil mozokot.

00:09:33.598 --> 00:09:35.598
Kako?

00:09:36.040 --> 00:09:38.040
Vreskanje.

00:09:38.720 --> 00:09:42.170
Nasilstvo, uzasna nedoverba.

00:09:42.378 --> 00:09:46.528
Site lekari se idioti
i se razbira jas najlosiot od niv.

00:09:46.724 --> 00:09:50.134
Se isfrlaa stvari, se gazea ocila.

00:09:50.374 --> 00:09:54.944
Ćena mu bese pritisnata do zid
i drzena za vrat.

00:09:57.331 --> 00:10:01.944
Saka mestoto da se dade
pod naem, duri da se prodade.

00:10:02.841 --> 00:10:09.071
Bratucetka vi, g-n Ŕsli,
e zena so silen instinkt i strast.

00:10:11.960 --> 00:10:13.960
Ěnogu silen.

00:10:15.011 --> 00:10:17.011
Razbirate li?

00:10:29.815 --> 00:10:31.832
Kade mu se rabotite?

00:10:33.560 --> 00:10:35.711
Oblekata, knigite.

00:10:36.894 --> 00:10:39.204
Denot posle pogrebot taa zamina.

00:10:40.038 --> 00:10:42.038
Neverojatna kucka.

00:10:43.937 --> 00:10:46.730
Rekov deka ocekuvav
so netrpenie da ja vidam.

00:10:49.366 --> 00:10:51.416
Se vikam Renaldi.

00:10:51.616 --> 00:10:53.952
Ŕdvokat i sovetnik sum mu na bratuced vi.

00:10:54.148 --> 00:10:56.558
Se nadevam i prijatel.
- Ěolam.

00:10:59.821 --> 00:11:02.551
Kopie od umrenicata.

00:11:02.921 --> 00:11:04.931
Edna vi bese isprateno vo Ŕnglija

00:11:05.131 --> 00:11:08.543
i edno na vasiot staratel po zelba
na Ŕmbrouz, vasiot kum,

00:11:08.871 --> 00:11:10.875
g-n Kendal.

00:11:13.106 --> 00:11:16.183
Znaete se za mene.
- Se razbira.

00:11:19.749 --> 00:11:22.559
Ima zabelezitelni nesta,
koi ce gi vidite tuka.

00:11:22.776 --> 00:11:25.906
Taka li?
- Örkvi, sliki.

00:11:26.763 --> 00:11:29.413
No pak...
- Sto?

00:11:29.713 --> 00:11:33.023
Vi se cinam kako nekoj
pozainteresiran za pivo i lisici,

00:11:33.223 --> 00:11:35.296
otkolku za renesansa.

00:11:36.376 --> 00:11:39.476
Ŕ zosto ne?
- Ne veruvam vo nisto, sto rekovte.

00:11:39.724 --> 00:11:42.834
Ěislam deka ako bev tuka,
bratuced mi uste ce bese ziv.

00:11:43.613 --> 00:11:46.103
Veruvam, deka sto i da go cinelo,

00:11:46.308 --> 00:11:48.738
bolkata i stradanjeto, pred da umre,

00:11:48.949 --> 00:11:52.249
ce go stovaram so seta sila

00:11:52.591 --> 00:11:55.591
vrz zenata, koja toa mu go pricini.

00:12:18.298 --> 00:12:20.588
Toj bese dobar covek, gospodaru Filip.

00:12:20.986 --> 00:12:23.076
Blagodaram, momcinja.

00:12:23.299 --> 00:12:25.649
Ŕjde, Źeriko,
daj mi go toa prokleto nesto.

00:12:25.860 --> 00:12:27.860
Sekogas si kosel kako devojce.

00:12:32.156 --> 00:12:34.252
Óste govedsko, gospodaru Filip?

00:12:35.880 --> 00:12:37.930
Gospodaru Filip?

00:12:38.244 --> 00:12:41.094
Sega vie ste gospodarot.

00:12:51.463 --> 00:12:54.462
Istiot testament,
koj go sostaviv pred 10 godini.

00:12:55.360 --> 00:12:57.930
Bez nikakvi klauzuli za soprugata.

00:12:58.126 --> 00:13:00.996
Siguren li si?
- Sosema.

00:13:01.245 --> 00:13:03.335
Go pregledav vnimatelno,

00:13:03.853 --> 00:13:07.243
kako i propratnoto pismo
od g-n Renaldi.

00:13:07.446 --> 00:13:11.636
Nikade ne e spomnata
pretenzija za delot na g-n Ŕsli.

00:13:12.298 --> 00:13:16.098
Izbezumen sum.
- Zosto?

00:13:16.269 --> 00:13:19.174
Znaes mnogu dobro,
deka taa go odnese vo smrt.

00:13:19.374 --> 00:13:21.453
Ne znaes takvo nesto.

00:13:22.035 --> 00:13:25.305
Ŕko govoris na ovoj nacin
za vdovicata na bratuced ti,

00:13:25.505 --> 00:13:27.599
iskreno kazano, ne sakam da slusam.

00:13:28.362 --> 00:13:30.432
Bese neverojaten srecnik.

00:13:31.084 --> 00:13:35.554
Öeliot imot ti go ostava tebe na tvojot
rodenden po zelba na Ŕmbrouz.

00:13:35.754 --> 00:13:38.595
Neli ne veruvas na site
tie gluposti za tumorot?

00:13:38.945 --> 00:13:44.045
Eve ja umrenicata
so objasnuvanje za smrtta.

00:13:45.295 --> 00:13:48.945
Kakov motiv moze da ima,
bez da dobie nisto od negovata smrt?

00:13:49.793 --> 00:13:53.230
Da, zosto da ne poveruvam?

00:13:54.993 --> 00:13:57.428
Ŕmbrouz ne mi bese tatko,

00:13:59.489 --> 00:14:01.489
no bese kako takov.

00:14:02.331 --> 00:14:05.903
Vsusnost, podobar od poveceto tatkovci.

00:14:07.029 --> 00:14:09.029
Na site ni nedostasuva.

00:14:12.670 --> 00:14:14.670
Ěene mi nedostasuva.

00:14:16.872 --> 00:14:19.222
Treba da znaete,
deka noviot gospodar Ŕsli,

00:14:19.422 --> 00:14:21.980
planira da prodolzi,
isto kako stariot.

00:14:41.950 --> 00:14:43.950
Taa e vo Ŕnglija.

00:14:45.776 --> 00:14:47.776
Tuka e.

00:14:49.181 --> 00:14:51.711
Ne bi se grizela.
Ťe pogleda na mestoto

00:14:51.911 --> 00:14:54.192
i se vraca nazad vo kocijata.
- Óbavo.

00:14:55.788 --> 00:14:58.438
Pogledni go ova, prav.

00:14:58.603 --> 00:15:01.753
Sama neka go izbrise, ako i preci.
- I ovaa mirizba.

00:15:01.936 --> 00:15:04.846
Sekoe kuce vo zemjata
li se praznelo tuka?

00:15:05.046 --> 00:15:07.141
Verojatno.
- Kade ce ja smestis?

00:15:07.368 --> 00:15:09.578
Vo sobata na Ŕmbrouz?
- Ne.

00:15:10.370 --> 00:15:12.441
Łas ce ja zemam.

00:15:13.618 --> 00:15:15.618
Taa moze da ja zeme sinata soba.

00:15:16.449 --> 00:15:19.319
Navistina? Ne e li nepropustliva?

00:15:29.994 --> 00:15:32.145
Treba potpolno da i pdgovara.

00:15:36.641 --> 00:15:38.641
Sto ce pravis so nea?

00:15:40.502 --> 00:15:42.502
Ťe se ispravam sproti nea.

00:15:43.540 --> 00:15:46.010
Se razbira ce se obide
da se razvika na izleguvanje

00:15:46.969 --> 00:15:50.559
ili ce pripadne.
- Kolku teatralno.

00:15:50.759 --> 00:15:53.985
Őisterija, ne e li toa, sto
covek go ocekuva od italijancite?

00:15:54.185 --> 00:15:56.228
Taa e samo pola italijanka.

00:15:58.315 --> 00:16:02.065
So site tie makaroni verojatno
e premnogu debela da se iskaci po skalite.

00:16:05.180 --> 00:16:08.891
Sakam spravedlivost za Ŕmbrouz.

00:16:09.886 --> 00:16:11.886
Ěislam, deka si iznerviran.

00:16:12.650 --> 00:16:14.660
Ni najmalku.

00:16:14.878 --> 00:16:17.588
Sakas li da ostanam?
- Sto imas vo predvid?

00:16:17.797 --> 00:16:19.887
Da bidam tuka.

00:16:20.105 --> 00:16:22.142
Vo koe vreme ja ocekuvas?

00:16:25.120 --> 00:16:27.120
Ěislam deka mozam da se spravam.

00:16:30.638 --> 00:16:34.668
Navistina si nervozen, neli?
- Sakam da sum sam.

00:16:51.187 --> 00:16:53.582
Izvini
- Nema problem.

00:16:55.155 --> 00:16:58.015
Razbiram.
- Ne, zalam.

00:17:00.200 --> 00:17:03.900
I ti blagodaram za se.

00:17:05.980 --> 00:17:08.630
Za cveceto, i sto se ponudi da ostanes.

00:17:09.271 --> 00:17:11.271
Se razbira.

00:17:11.720 --> 00:17:13.720
So sreca.

00:17:14.910 --> 00:17:17.164
Obidi se da ne ja zadusis pred vecera.

00:17:23.436 --> 00:17:25.806
Óveri se, deka si ja ceka vecerata,

00:17:25.988 --> 00:17:29.658
deka ja zadrzuva gladta, dodeka
gospodarot na kucata se vrati

00:17:29.858 --> 00:17:31.929
Łasno li e?
- Kako den.

00:17:32.160 --> 00:17:34.177
Dobro, pogrizi se za toa.

00:18:35.280 --> 00:18:38.250
Taa e tuka.
- Bez bagaz?

00:18:38.494 --> 00:18:41.812
Nestata na gospodarot Ŕmbrouz
bea staveni vo vasata stara soba.

00:18:48.236 --> 00:18:50.986
Taa kade e sega?
- Vo nejzinata soba.

00:18:51.186 --> 00:18:53.197
Vo nejzinata soba.

00:18:54.360 --> 00:18:57.280
Veli deka e umorna
i moli da ja izvinite za vecerata.

00:19:01.976 --> 00:19:03.976
Kade po davolite se kucinjata?

00:19:05.900 --> 00:19:07.935
Ěislam deka ja sledea nagore.

00:19:13.600 --> 00:19:15.637
Kakva bese do Boga?

00:19:17.069 --> 00:19:19.069
Ne mozam da kazam, ser.

00:19:20.341 --> 00:19:22.911
Do Boga, covece? Debela ili slaba?

00:19:23.704 --> 00:19:27.120
Visoka, niska?
Ima li drvena noga?

00:19:28.914 --> 00:19:32.464
Ěustaci?
Ima li bradavica na nosot?

00:19:33.238 --> 00:19:35.389
Ne znam nisto za toa, ser.

00:19:49.952 --> 00:19:52.082
Gospodata isprati soopstenie,

00:19:52.293 --> 00:19:55.483
deka sigurno sakate
da ja pozdravite,

00:19:55.683 --> 00:19:57.685
koga ce vecerate.

00:19:57.978 --> 00:20:01.367
Ťe se raduva da ve primi, ser.

00:20:06.400 --> 00:20:08.400
Blagodaram, Sijkamb.

00:20:14.684 --> 00:20:16.780
Toa e, Sijkamb, blagodaram.

00:20:57.199 --> 00:20:59.199
Vlezi.

00:21:11.831 --> 00:21:13.851
Ŕmbrouz...

00:21:20.679 --> 00:21:22.769
Ěnogu zalam.

00:21:23.548 --> 00:21:27.378
Ne ocekuvav da licate
tolku na bratuced vi.

00:21:34.833 --> 00:21:38.304
Nema li da sednete za moment?

00:21:41.853 --> 00:21:43.853
Sakate li caj?

00:21:45.752 --> 00:21:47.752
Stom sakate.

00:21:55.675 --> 00:21:59.525
Razumno li e da go pravam toa?
Od kade ste?

00:22:00.290 --> 00:22:02.380
Toa e samo casa caj.

00:22:02.580 --> 00:22:04.900
Iznenaden sum,
sto znaat kako da gi pravat.

00:22:08.925 --> 00:22:11.875
Ěasloto se topi.

00:22:12.085 --> 00:22:15.135
Podobro izlizete si gi prstite.

00:22:31.436 --> 00:22:33.436
Pusete, ako sakate.

00:22:33.844 --> 00:22:37.194
Sijkamb smeta deka toa ne e vo red.
Ťe go namirisa nautro.

00:22:37.394 --> 00:22:39.631
Ťe go otvoram prozorecot pred da legnam.

00:22:39.831 --> 00:22:42.570
Dozdot ce vleze vnatre
i ce go osteti vasiot nov cilim.

00:22:42.770 --> 00:22:44.839
Kolku ste prebirliv.

00:22:45.039 --> 00:22:47.573
Ěislev deka se grizite za takvi nesta.

00:22:47.773 --> 00:22:49.866
Nie?
- Ćenite.

00:22:50.066 --> 00:22:52.760
Samo, koga nema za sto
drugo da se grizime.

00:22:55.973 --> 00:23:00.083
Izgleda nikoj ne bil tuka,
otkako nekoja si tetka Fibi...

00:23:00.281 --> 00:23:03.411
Koja se vljubila vo svestenik,
koj sto ne ja sakal vo zamena.

00:23:03.611 --> 00:23:06.971
Zaminala za Tuni bridz Vels
da go izleci svoeto raneto srce.

00:23:07.171 --> 00:23:09.358
Ŕmbrouz ne vi li ja
raskazuval istorijata?

00:23:09.558 --> 00:23:11.596
Ne.

00:23:11.796 --> 00:23:14.633
Zemala sedativi vo traenje od 20 godini,

00:23:14.833 --> 00:23:19.701
i togas odnovo se vljubila
na prv pogled vo drug svestenik.

00:23:21.647 --> 00:23:25.517
Slava na nebesata, toj ja zasakal.
- Da, slava Bogu.

00:23:25.728 --> 00:23:28.600
Taa pocinala na svojata bracna noc.

00:23:29.642 --> 00:23:31.642
Od sto?

00:23:32.309 --> 00:23:35.425
Od stres, mislam.

00:23:43.798 --> 00:23:48.308
Ěislam deka go izmislivte.
- Nisto slicno, prasajte go Sijkamb.

00:23:53.503 --> 00:23:56.874
Ótre moze da iznajmam konj
i da pogledam naokolu.

00:23:57.840 --> 00:24:02.250
Takvo cudno cuvstvo.
Patuvajci do kucata,

00:24:02.450 --> 00:24:04.972
a Sijkamb stoese do vratata,
za da me preceka.

00:24:05.224 --> 00:24:08.044
Sum go pravela tolku pati
vo svojata fantazija.

00:24:09.304 --> 00:24:11.834
Casovnikot udri, koga zaprevme.

00:24:13.667 --> 00:24:17.046
Izgleda, duri go raspoznavam
zvukot na kambanata.

00:24:35.224 --> 00:24:37.254
Ómoren ste.
- Ne sum.

00:24:37.484 --> 00:24:40.994
Skoro spiete.
- Ne sum umoren, navistina.

00:24:41.208 --> 00:24:44.918
Ěolam, prestanete da bidete taka fin,
stanete i odite da si legnete.

00:24:45.112 --> 00:24:48.483
Se razbira. Izvinete.

00:24:52.713 --> 00:24:54.743
Ćalam.
- Leka noc!

00:25:00.503 --> 00:25:02.503
Piter Velc.

00:25:05.863 --> 00:25:07.863
Piter Velc.

00:25:24.567 --> 00:25:26.604
Dobro utro.
- Dobro utro.

00:25:30.825 --> 00:25:35.395
Toa e livadata Bouden.
Ŕ toa zalivot Kemp.

00:25:37.000 --> 00:25:40.270
Parket Bif. Bion Őil.

00:25:40.423 --> 00:25:42.513
Nevozmozno e.

00:25:42.713 --> 00:25:46.393
Ŕ vo dalecinata so raloto vo nego
e Zapadniot rid,

00:25:46.712 --> 00:25:48.809
a otade nego Istocniot.

00:25:53.034 --> 00:25:55.310
Za sto drugo mislevte,
deka si zboruvavme?

00:25:57.270 --> 00:25:59.280
Ocigledno, nemam pretstava.

00:25:59.434 --> 00:26:02.708
Seto ova, bese negovata strast.

00:26:05.241 --> 00:26:07.241
Zatoa go pretvoriv i vo moja strast.

00:26:41.269 --> 00:26:44.979
Site ce ve zagleduvaat.
- Togas ce gi zagleduvam i jas.

00:26:51.645 --> 00:26:53.645
Tuka sme.

00:26:58.948 --> 00:27:00.948
Negovite umstveni sposobnosti,

00:27:01.291 --> 00:27:03.891
sa pretvoreni vo vezbi,

00:27:04.135 --> 00:27:07.925
vo cvrsta nasoka na golem
i navlekuvacki interes.

00:27:08.174 --> 00:27:11.644
Vnimanieto mu reagira
na mnozestvo veselbi,

00:27:11.860 --> 00:27:13.950
vo koi mozel da otkaci.

00:27:18.382 --> 00:27:20.432
Toa bese lesno.

00:27:20.673 --> 00:27:23.963
Se plasev, deka moze da e pricina...
- Óbava ceremonija.

00:27:24.309 --> 00:27:26.759
Vo onoj den, koga padna samrakot,

00:27:26.926 --> 00:27:31.476
oracite na seloto go vlecea
plugot od vrata na vrata

00:27:31.665 --> 00:27:36.075
i molea za besplaten pijalok,
a toa e golem plug,

00:27:36.275 --> 00:27:38.408
Vlecen od dva ubavi vola.
- Boze!

00:28:08.616 --> 00:28:10.651
Bravo.

00:28:24.834 --> 00:28:26.834
<i>Eden angel pominuva...</i>

00:28:27.842 --> 00:28:32.052
Kazi go pak.
- Pominuva angel.

00:28:41.427 --> 00:28:45.117
Koj ce mi se pridruzi
vo pienjeto na ova ubavo vino?

00:28:45.290 --> 00:28:48.360
Osven, ako mazite sakaat
da se povlecat vo drugata soba,

00:28:48.560 --> 00:28:50.626
dodeka nie gi pusime lulite.

00:28:55.932 --> 00:28:58.002
Blagodaram za prekrasniot den.

00:28:58.261 --> 00:29:01.371
Luiz, blagodaram za cveceto.

00:29:01.601 --> 00:29:03.931
Óbavi cvecinja!
- Poveli pak!

00:29:05.136 --> 00:29:08.066
Podobro pobrzaj
i ozeni se za tvojata Luiz,

00:29:08.266 --> 00:29:10.968
pred da ja grabne nekoj drug.

00:29:11.168 --> 00:29:14.083
Ne e "mojata" Luiz.
- Taka li?

00:29:14.441 --> 00:29:16.598
Izgleda tatko i ima drugi idei.

00:29:17.708 --> 00:29:20.378
Zosto site pretpostavuvaat,
deka so Luiz ce se zememe?

00:29:20.578 --> 00:29:22.881
Kreni gi nozete.
- Ćalam.

00:29:26.735 --> 00:29:29.645
Te smeta za mnogu ubava.
- Navistina li?

00:29:30.988 --> 00:29:33.198
Kako sto pravat devojcinjata Paskoa.

00:29:33.491 --> 00:29:35.491
Ózasno laskavo.

00:29:35.766 --> 00:29:40.116
Pastorot ne e soglasen.
- Ěili Boze.

00:29:40.937 --> 00:29:43.547
No te smeta za zenstvena.
- Kreni gi nozete.

00:29:43.747 --> 00:29:46.672
"Krajno zenstvena,"
bea negovite zborovi.

00:29:46.854 --> 00:29:49.788
Se prasuvam po kakov nacin.

00:29:50.548 --> 00:29:53.618
Pretpostavuvam po takov,
koj sto e poinakov za g-da Paskoa.

00:29:54.106 --> 00:29:57.156
I kako bi ja opredelil?
- Da opredelam sto?

00:29:57.356 --> 00:30:00.213
Razlikata. Nasata zenstvenost.

00:30:00.812 --> 00:30:03.043
Taa na g-da Paskoa i mojata.

00:30:05.412 --> 00:30:07.412
Bog znae.

00:30:07.669 --> 00:30:11.604
Znam samo, deka mi se dopada da te gledam,

00:30:13.631 --> 00:30:15.791
no ne mi se dopada da ja gledam g-da Paskoa.

00:30:21.868 --> 00:30:24.918
Site tie izmislici
da ostanes vo Pelin.

00:30:25.265 --> 00:30:27.335
Sto ima, za da ne ostanes tuka?

00:30:27.535 --> 00:30:30.050
Ťe ostanam dodeka na Sijkamb
mu pisne od mene.

00:30:30.250 --> 00:30:34.356
Toj nema nisto opsto so toa.
- Ili ce mi svrsat parite.

00:30:34.556 --> 00:30:38.315
Prinudena sum da davam casovi
po italijanski na dosadni soprugi.

00:30:38.617 --> 00:30:42.287
Ne, samo starite momi predavaat.
Site go znaat toa.

00:30:42.603 --> 00:30:45.873
Samo, koga nekoj gi poddrzuva.
- Ŕ vdovicite?

00:30:46.048 --> 00:30:49.978
Tie li? Ťe se omazat sto e mozno najbrzo.

00:30:50.178 --> 00:30:53.888
Ŕko ne mozat da go napravat toa,
gi zalozuvaat svoite vencalni burmi.

00:30:59.640 --> 00:31:03.051
Ěislam deka pretpocitam
da davam casovi po italijanski.

00:31:03.930 --> 00:31:05.930
Leka noc, Filip.

00:31:10.283 --> 00:31:12.340
Idiot.

00:31:14.425 --> 00:31:16.425
Idiot.

00:31:16.796 --> 00:31:18.806
Sto ce i dademe?

00:31:19.005 --> 00:31:22.082
Pomisli za suma, koja ja smetas
za spravedliva i razumna.

00:31:26.280 --> 00:31:28.310
Ěnogu dobro.
- Zavrsi li?

00:31:28.510 --> 00:31:30.534
Vo glavata ti e li?
- Da.

00:31:31.512 --> 00:31:33.566
Dupliraj ja.

00:31:34.344 --> 00:31:36.934
Ŕko go napravime,
treba da e kako sto treba.

00:31:37.134 --> 00:31:39.523
Kako Ŕmbrouz bi go napravil.
- Kako sto sakas.

00:31:40.348 --> 00:31:42.378
Napisi pismo.
- Sega li?

00:31:43.732 --> 00:31:45.742
Te ocekuvavme li denes?

00:31:46.000 --> 00:31:48.696
Łas...
- Ťe zemes li nesto?

00:31:49.280 --> 00:31:52.750
Łas... Blagodaram.
- Ti dade li kafe?

00:31:52.972 --> 00:31:56.062
Drago mi e da te vidam vesela.
- Sto imas vo predvid?

00:31:56.318 --> 00:31:59.775
Vcera site izgledavte nesrecni.

00:32:00.671 --> 00:32:02.721
Izbezumena sum, sto si zabelezal.

00:32:02.945 --> 00:32:06.875
Site vidovme. Iznenaden sum,
sto devojcinjata Paskoa ne zabelezaa.

00:32:07.040 --> 00:32:10.690
Verojatno bea premnogu zafateni,
zabelezuvajci nesto drugo.

00:32:10.935 --> 00:32:13.465
Sto?
- Kolku lesno treba da e,

00:32:13.665 --> 00:32:17.497
za zeni kako bratucetka ti Rejcel
da te vrti na maliot prst.

00:32:24.040 --> 00:32:26.040
Davaj.

00:32:31.319 --> 00:32:33.470
Kade e taa?
- Vo kujnata.

00:32:37.372 --> 00:32:40.187
Sto pravi?
- Tesko e da se kaze.

00:32:44.235 --> 00:32:46.235
Se nadevam, deka nemas protiv.

00:32:46.939 --> 00:32:48.939
Voopsto ne.

00:32:49.481 --> 00:32:51.551
Sto e?
- Caj od bilki.

00:32:51.720 --> 00:32:55.930
Italijanski caj,
mesavini napraveni od ovie bilki.

00:32:56.130 --> 00:32:58.219
Ete, probaj.

00:32:58.468 --> 00:33:00.468
Probaj.

00:33:09.722 --> 00:33:13.320
Odvratno e.

00:33:14.564 --> 00:33:16.854
Dobro e za tebe, za tvoeto zdravje.

00:33:18.380 --> 00:33:20.380
Kade bese?

00:33:21.318 --> 00:33:23.318
Nadvor i naokolu.

00:33:26.268 --> 00:33:28.338
Si go nateral da go napise toa!

00:33:28.498 --> 00:33:30.548
Sto?

00:33:30.724 --> 00:33:34.734
Nema takvo nesto.
- Ŕko si imal namera da me ponizis,

00:33:34.934 --> 00:33:37.355
ne mozese li da zapocnes podobro?

00:33:37.555 --> 00:33:40.628
Zosto?
- Kako da sum dosla da molam.

00:33:40.799 --> 00:33:44.589
No ne si go napravila toa.
- Ne moze li sama da se potrudam?

00:33:45.066 --> 00:33:48.316
Ćena, koja si go prokrcuva patot
vo ovoj svet, kako sto taa saka.

00:33:48.950 --> 00:33:52.500
Ne gledas li, deka ako ti gi sakav parite,
ce ti gi pobarav?

00:33:52.700 --> 00:33:54.762
Ne razbiras li, deka bese prosto...

00:33:54.962 --> 00:33:58.448
Bese sega za lekciite po italijanski.
- Ŕko ne bese?

00:33:58.663 --> 00:34:00.833
Ima li nesto taka uzasno
sramno vo toa?

00:34:01.040 --> 00:34:04.170
Da! Ti si sopruga na Ŕmbrouz.

00:34:04.640 --> 00:34:07.850
Łas, negoviot naslednik,
nema da go dozvolam toa. Razbiras li?

00:34:08.387 --> 00:34:13.760
Prosto nema da go dozvolam.
Razbiras li?

00:34:29.024 --> 00:34:31.024
Boze!

00:34:38.974 --> 00:34:41.045
Podobro odnesi i nesto.

00:35:20.177 --> 00:35:22.177
Filip.

00:35:23.275 --> 00:35:25.275
Te razbudiv li?

00:35:27.080 --> 00:35:29.080
Ne.

00:35:35.108 --> 00:35:37.108
Blagodaram za beleskata.

00:35:41.035 --> 00:35:43.730
Bev zbrkana.

00:35:44.350 --> 00:35:46.350
Ćalam.

00:35:49.691 --> 00:35:52.929
Bi pretpocital da me udris,
otkolku da te slusnam da places.

00:35:58.403 --> 00:36:03.893
Ěajka mi pocina,
pred da mozam da pametam.

00:36:04.069 --> 00:36:06.069
Ne sum videl zena da place.

00:36:08.155 --> 00:36:10.155
Ťe ja prifatam izdrskata.

00:36:12.423 --> 00:36:15.723
So blagodarnost,
no ce treba da zaminam.

00:36:18.760 --> 00:36:20.797
Za da otides kade?
- Ne e vazno.

00:36:21.853 --> 00:36:24.223
Ěislev deka ti se dopada da si tuka.

00:36:25.060 --> 00:36:27.416
Bese uctiva li?
- Ne bidi glupak.

00:36:29.268 --> 00:36:32.878
Ŕko Ŕmbrouz ne bese takov idiot,
ova mesto ce bese tvoj dom.

00:36:33.074 --> 00:36:35.164
Ěislam deka jas sum idiotkata.

00:36:35.518 --> 00:36:38.652
Ěislev deka doadajci tuka,
ce go vratam nazad vo zivotot.

00:36:51.184 --> 00:36:53.779
Ne znam zosto dojde.

00:36:55.840 --> 00:36:57.840
Ne znam nisto za tebe.

00:36:59.638 --> 00:37:02.358
Znam samo, deka mi se dopada da si tuka.

00:37:04.068 --> 00:37:06.068
I ne sakam da si odis.

00:37:07.200 --> 00:37:09.200
Slozeno li e?

00:37:09.640 --> 00:37:12.990
Ěnogu.
- Ŕko sakas da si otides, odi si.

00:37:13.348 --> 00:37:15.398
Ťe predizvika mnogu prikaski.

00:37:15.598 --> 00:37:17.930
Ěislev, deka ce bidat mnogu povece,
ako ostanam.

00:37:19.505 --> 00:37:23.035
Treba da govoram so tvojot kum.
- Toa ne e negova griza.

00:37:23.528 --> 00:37:26.998
Ima samo eden problem i toa e,
sakas li da ostanes ili ne?

00:37:27.198 --> 00:37:30.049
Kako moze da me prasuvas?
Go znaes odgovorot.

00:37:30.249 --> 00:37:35.715
Ne go znam i vo toa e problemot.

00:37:37.560 --> 00:37:39.560
Ťe ostanes li?

00:37:40.655 --> 00:37:43.045
Barem za kratko?
- Ťe ostanam.

00:37:44.040 --> 00:37:47.930
Da, za malku.

00:37:48.840 --> 00:37:51.030
Togas ce ti kazam leka noc.
- Leka noc.

00:37:51.255 --> 00:37:53.325
Se nadevam deka ce pospies.
- Ti isto.

00:37:53.525 --> 00:37:56.328
I da ne si mi luta.
- Ne ti bev luta, Filip.

00:37:56.540 --> 00:37:58.640
Ela tuka.

00:38:03.493 --> 00:38:05.493
Navedni se.

00:38:12.089 --> 00:38:15.060
Sega legni si kako dobro momce.
Odi.

00:38:35.258 --> 00:38:37.308
Gotova e.
- Da, gledam.

00:38:37.908 --> 00:38:40.278
Nesto za postata?
- Da.

00:38:40.482 --> 00:38:43.292
Vsusnost, zosto ne mi go
ostavis mene, Vilington?

00:38:43.508 --> 00:38:46.424
Ěoze da go ostavi po pat.
- Ěnogu dobro, ser.

00:38:59.916 --> 00:39:01.916
Pobrzaj.

00:39:15.320 --> 00:39:20.237
Toa e caj od bilki napraven
so kopar i sipka.

00:39:20.898 --> 00:39:24.888
Zaedno, ce te nateraat
da se pocuvstvuvas podobro.

00:39:25.719 --> 00:39:27.789
Ťe te pomislat za vestica.

00:39:27.989 --> 00:39:31.846
Ili poloso, ce te vikat srede
noc da gi poradas bebinjata.

00:39:32.046 --> 00:39:34.893
Bilniot caj sluzi i za toa.
- Gledas li, vestica.

00:39:35.060 --> 00:39:37.070
Zosto zenite da stradaat pri radanje?

00:39:37.778 --> 00:39:39.828
Toa li im e sudbinata?

00:39:40.069 --> 00:39:42.939
Ne sum mislel za toa.
- Se razbira, deka ne si.

00:39:43.090 --> 00:39:45.090
Ne znaes nisto za zenite.

00:39:51.336 --> 00:39:54.466
Se nadevam, deka ne sum kazala
nesto, so koe da te povredam.

00:39:54.666 --> 00:39:57.426
Nisto.
- Sto ima, Filip? Kazi mi?

00:40:01.578 --> 00:40:03.578
Te molam.

00:40:38.656 --> 00:40:41.435
Treba sama da go procetas
od vnatre na plikot.

00:40:47.641 --> 00:40:51.711
<i>"Najposle go napravi.
Rejcel, mojata tortura.</i>

00:40:53.141 --> 00:40:55.141
<i>Te molam, ela brzo."</i>

00:41:13.713 --> 00:41:15.723
Si me zamrazil.

00:41:18.720 --> 00:41:20.720
Da.

00:41:25.252 --> 00:41:27.252
Toa ne e potrebno.

00:41:29.608 --> 00:41:31.608
Ti ne si zenata, koja ja zamraziv.

00:41:42.459 --> 00:41:47.109
Ŕko ne gi sakas da gi ostavime
na ludeto koi ziveat vo imotot,

00:41:47.309 --> 00:41:49.541
koi sakaa da mu ja zemat oblekata?

00:41:50.230 --> 00:41:52.230
Toa e cudesna ideja.

00:42:06.280 --> 00:42:08.280
Sto da pravime so seto toa?

00:42:11.006 --> 00:42:14.356
Ne znam.
- Ěozes li da nosis nesto od toa?

00:42:17.123 --> 00:42:19.123
Ne.

00:42:20.635 --> 00:42:23.687
Cuvstvuvam, kako tukusto da mu go
otvorivme kovcegot.

00:42:25.961 --> 00:42:27.961
I se zagleduvame vo nego.

00:42:36.105 --> 00:42:38.105
Rejcel.

00:43:02.384 --> 00:43:04.384
Se e vo red. Ne placi.

00:43:04.720 --> 00:43:06.790
Ne placi. Se e vo red.

00:43:32.318 --> 00:43:34.648
Ne sakam taa da znae.
- Ser?

00:43:35.060 --> 00:43:37.060
Za drvoto.

00:43:37.963 --> 00:43:40.723
Sakam da e iznenaduvanje.
- Ěnogu dobro.

00:43:41.186 --> 00:43:45.062
Ne taka, prokleti nekadarnici.

00:43:45.560 --> 00:43:47.560
Se e iskriveno!

00:43:48.096 --> 00:43:51.086
Izvinete, ser.
- Nema nisto. Kade e taa?

00:43:51.786 --> 00:43:53.786
Vo sobata.

00:43:54.094 --> 00:43:58.404
Lica na krivata kula vo Piza.
Ispravete go.

00:43:58.857 --> 00:44:00.857
Vlezi.

00:44:02.174 --> 00:44:05.034
Ti si. Ne gledaj.

00:44:05.356 --> 00:44:07.406
Ěavni se.

00:44:08.405 --> 00:44:11.243
Ěi treba nesto posebno, g-n Kauc.

00:44:13.100 --> 00:44:15.100
Ne se ubavi li?

00:44:15.846 --> 00:44:17.916
Ne sum videl takvi.

00:44:18.116 --> 00:44:20.866
Najubavite od celata
kolekcija, bez somnenie.

00:44:23.498 --> 00:44:25.852
Nikoj ne gi nosel 25 godini.

00:44:27.802 --> 00:44:29.839
Ne i od svadbata na majka vi.

00:44:37.206 --> 00:44:41.076
Sega gi sakam.
- Razumno li e? Ŕko se izgubat?

00:44:41.276 --> 00:44:43.278
Nema da se izgubat, g-n Kauc.

00:44:43.676 --> 00:44:46.226
Ŕko se grizite sto
ce kaze mojot kum,

00:44:46.447 --> 00:44:48.697
bidete siguren,
deka sosema go odobruva.

00:44:48.857 --> 00:44:52.147
I pokraj toa, kako advokat
na semejstvoto niz godinite,

00:44:52.347 --> 00:44:54.552
bi pretpocital g-n Kendal da prisustvuva.

00:44:54.752 --> 00:44:57.109
Kako sto kazav, nego go nema.

00:45:06.575 --> 00:45:08.585
Źon?
- Ser.

00:45:08.785 --> 00:45:11.325
Odnesi go toa na g-data, ako sakas.

00:45:13.363 --> 00:45:15.363
Ěnogu dobro, ser.

00:46:14.840 --> 00:46:16.840
Blagodaram.

00:46:45.760 --> 00:46:47.760
Blagodaram.

00:47:06.960 --> 00:47:09.550
Dobra vecer.
- Dobra vecer.

00:47:14.600 --> 00:47:16.600
Tolku e ubavo.

00:47:39.406 --> 00:47:42.506
<i>Imase tri garvana na drvoto.</i>

00:47:46.580 --> 00:47:50.690
<i>Prviot veli:
"Sto e toa, sto gledam?"</i>

00:47:50.890 --> 00:47:54.637
<i>Tamu mrtov maz lezi.</i>

00:47:58.448 --> 00:48:02.658
<i>Site na negovata stara grada ce sedneme.</i>

00:48:06.000 --> 00:48:09.890
<i>Site na negovata stara grada ce sedneme.</i>

00:48:10.615 --> 00:48:12.615
Timoti.

00:48:14.679 --> 00:48:16.679
Źefri.

00:48:20.890 --> 00:48:22.890
Pastor Paskoa.

00:48:43.033 --> 00:48:45.063
Blagodaram za podarocite.

00:48:47.251 --> 00:48:50.150
Cao, Belinda. So uspeő utre.

00:48:58.120 --> 00:49:00.660
Kade se drugite?
- Gore, mislam.

00:49:04.813 --> 00:49:07.306
Drago mi e na moznosta da zboruvame.

00:49:09.537 --> 00:49:12.667
Da?
- Dobiv vesti od bankata.

00:49:14.102 --> 00:49:17.792
Da.
- Nekoi dosta voznemiruvacki.

00:49:21.829 --> 00:49:26.362
Bratucetka ti vece go nadmina
kreditot na svojata smetka.

00:49:28.429 --> 00:49:31.399
Ěozam samo da mislam,
deka pracala pari nadvor od zemjata.

00:49:32.745 --> 00:49:34.814
Komu?

00:49:35.425 --> 00:49:37.515
Gluposti, ne.

00:49:38.748 --> 00:49:40.802
Samo e darezliva.

00:49:41.544 --> 00:49:43.574
Ovaa vecer, naprimer, ti vide.

00:49:44.414 --> 00:49:46.544
Podarok za sekoe semejstvo vo sobata.

00:49:46.703 --> 00:49:49.713
Toa ne e pricina
za overdraft vo takva golemina.

00:49:49.913 --> 00:49:53.544
Seto toa, tkaeninite, zavesite.
- Samo li pazaruvanjeto...

00:49:53.744 --> 00:49:55.821
Prosto zgolemi ja izdrskata.

00:49:59.435 --> 00:50:01.435
Da ja zgolemam?
- Da.

00:50:03.763 --> 00:50:05.763
Pokrij go overdraftot.

00:50:09.212 --> 00:50:11.543
Se potrasprasav malku naokolu.

00:50:13.255 --> 00:50:16.525
Duelot, pri koj sto
nejziniot prv soprug zaginal,

00:50:16.725 --> 00:50:18.990
bil voden medu eden od
nejzinite ljubovnici?

00:50:19.190 --> 00:50:22.745
Ne veruvam.
- So losa slava se toj i taa

00:50:23.294 --> 00:50:25.525
za neobuzdano rasipnost

00:50:26.235 --> 00:50:29.706
i ocevidno bezgranicen

00:50:31.600 --> 00:50:33.600
apetit.

00:50:38.331 --> 00:50:40.331
Razbiras li?

00:50:43.040 --> 00:50:45.040
Razbiras li?

00:50:50.620 --> 00:50:56.110
Ne sum mislel, deka ce padnes tolku
nisko, da slusas takvi ozboruvanja.

00:50:58.975 --> 00:51:01.505
Nemase pravo da ja zemas ogrlicata.

00:51:01.788 --> 00:51:03.838
Ěoja e. Od ovoj imot e.

00:51:04.008 --> 00:51:06.418
Imotot uste ne e tvoj,
dobro znaes.

00:51:06.617 --> 00:51:08.617
Sto od toa. Brzo ce bide.

00:51:10.051 --> 00:51:14.901
Treba da te zamolam
taa da ja vrati ogrlicata.

00:51:15.071 --> 00:51:17.071
Zarem?

00:51:17.334 --> 00:51:20.691
Toa e poslednoto na svetot,
sto imam namera da go napravam.

00:51:21.637 --> 00:51:24.037
Togas jas treba
da go napravam mesto tebe.

00:51:25.246 --> 00:51:27.336
Proklet da sum, ako go napravis.

00:51:27.532 --> 00:51:29.532
Eve.

00:51:31.520 --> 00:51:33.530
Luiz mi objasni.

00:51:33.680 --> 00:51:35.950
Sosema ste prav
da pobarate da ja vratam.

00:51:36.130 --> 00:51:38.704
Ne.
- Te molam, Filip.

00:51:39.504 --> 00:51:43.854
Bese golema cest da ja nosam
na takva specijalna vecer. Blagodaram.

00:51:44.054 --> 00:51:48.051
Sakam da ja nosis sekoja vecer.
- Da gi spakuvam li?

00:51:48.680 --> 00:51:50.750
Ne, blagodaram.

00:51:54.394 --> 00:51:57.184
Ťe zalis zatoa.
Glupak.

00:51:57.353 --> 00:52:01.003
Blagodaram za ubavata
i uspesna vecer, Filip.

00:52:01.900 --> 00:52:04.950
Da se nadevame tanuavnjero
da ne ve drzi buden cela noc.

00:52:05.965 --> 00:52:09.135
Na dvajcata vi pozeluvam
srecen Bozik.

00:52:09.334 --> 00:52:11.344
I vam, vesel Bozik.

00:52:11.502 --> 00:52:13.832
Vesel Bozik.
- Vesel Bozik, Luis.

00:52:14.856 --> 00:52:17.286
Leka noc, Filip.
- Vesel Bozik, Filip.

00:52:17.527 --> 00:52:20.097
Leka noc.
- Odnovo blagodaram.

00:52:40.886 --> 00:52:43.037
Sakav ti da ja nosis.

00:52:45.471 --> 00:52:47.501
Da ja poseduvas.

00:52:47.741 --> 00:52:49.811
Ěolci.
- Se se rasipa.

00:52:50.046 --> 00:52:52.645
Ěajka mi gi nosese ovie perli
na denot na svadbata.

00:52:55.022 --> 00:52:57.022
I baba mi.

00:52:57.558 --> 00:52:59.558
I nejzinata majka pred nea.

00:53:01.372 --> 00:53:04.382
Zatoa bev taka gorda
i srecna da gi nosam.

00:53:04.764 --> 00:53:09.034
Ŕko bev omazena tuka,
a ne vo Italija i jas ce gi nosev.

00:53:11.919 --> 00:53:16.609
Ne taguvaj.
Vesel Bozik, drag Filip.

00:53:16.809 --> 00:53:20.083
Treba da se vracame na zabavata,
zatoa sto gostite ne cekaat.

00:53:20.741 --> 00:53:22.741
Vesel Bozik, Filip.

00:53:25.320 --> 00:53:27.630
Zapravo nakitot e tvoj.

00:53:28.480 --> 00:53:32.730
Ne samo toj, se.
Siguren sum, deka ima testament.

00:53:32.930 --> 00:53:35.793
Imase, no ne bese potpisan.

00:53:36.000 --> 00:53:38.330
Kaj tebe li e? Ěoze li da go vidam?

00:53:38.966 --> 00:53:41.796
Se ti ostava.
- No ne e potpisano.

00:53:45.405 --> 00:53:47.681
Toa e negoviot rakopis.

00:53:48.061 --> 00:53:51.391
Łanuari, znaes li zosto go izbral
da go napravi testamentot?

00:53:51.591 --> 00:53:53.676
Ŕ potoa da ne go potpise?

00:53:55.554 --> 00:53:57.554
Izgubiv dete.

00:53:59.960 --> 00:54:03.000
I nesto drugo zagina isto.
- Sto?

00:54:04.120 --> 00:54:07.610
Nadezta. Ne znam.

00:54:07.960 --> 00:54:10.998
Negovata verba vo mene, vo nas.

00:54:12.920 --> 00:54:14.920
Łas go razbolev.

00:54:16.720 --> 00:54:18.720
Ne sum se cuvstvuvala poosamena.

00:54:21.539 --> 00:54:26.170
Eden den se razbudiv i otkriv,

00:54:30.668 --> 00:54:32.683
deka ziveam so nepoznat,

00:54:35.426 --> 00:54:37.426
koj sto me mrazese

00:54:38.814 --> 00:54:40.814
i sakase da me povredi.

00:54:47.706 --> 00:54:51.663
Nema gorclivi cuvstva vo ovaa kuca.

00:54:53.160 --> 00:54:55.160
Sega mestoto ti e tuka.

00:54:57.854 --> 00:54:59.854
Tocno kako sto go napisal.

00:55:06.240 --> 00:55:08.240
Blagodaram.

00:55:09.280 --> 00:55:13.250
Izgleda nema naredba
g-da Ŕsli da se omazi odnovo.

00:55:13.600 --> 00:55:17.830
Toa nema da se sluci.
- Problemot treba da se resi, neli?

00:55:18.855 --> 00:55:20.855
Ŕko nastojuvate.

00:55:22.775 --> 00:55:25.945
Vo slucaj da se omazi,
nejzinata sopstvenost se vraca kaj vas,

00:55:26.145 --> 00:55:28.190
osven, ako ne pocinete pred nea?

00:55:29.211 --> 00:55:32.242
Da, odlicno.

00:55:32.761 --> 00:55:36.731
Pedanten ste za tie nesta,
nali, g-n Kauc?

00:55:36.926 --> 00:55:40.920
Toa mi e rabota, g-n Ŕsli,
se da sledam striktno.

00:55:44.200 --> 00:55:49.110
Sakate da e gotovo i izgotveno
oficijalno do vasiot 25-ti rodenden?

00:55:49.407 --> 00:55:52.257
Da, denta koga sopstvenosta
mi preminuva mene.

00:55:54.420 --> 00:55:56.860
Postapuvate mnogu darezlivo,
ako mozam da kazam.

00:55:58.488 --> 00:56:01.398
Se otkazuvate od se vo migot,
koga stanuva vase.

00:56:02.366 --> 00:56:04.587
Darezlivo, moze da se kaze,
do momentot na...

00:56:06.982 --> 00:56:08.982
Nerazumnost?

00:56:09.922 --> 00:56:11.922
Ťe napravite li sto pobarav?

00:56:43.986 --> 00:56:45.986
Filip.

00:56:47.462 --> 00:56:49.462
Imame gost.

00:56:51.145 --> 00:56:54.195
Kakvo iznenaduvanje.
- Kolku ubava kuca.

00:56:54.530 --> 00:56:57.860
Se nadevam deka nemate protiv,
sto bratucetka vi me proseta.

00:56:58.060 --> 00:57:01.067
Ěnogu pogolema e,
otkolku sto mi dozvolija da mislam.

00:57:01.267 --> 00:57:05.068
Benito Kastelucio ti donese ogromen
buket cvece. Kozimo bese besen.

00:57:42.109 --> 00:57:44.180
Dojdov da ti posakam leka noc.

00:57:45.475 --> 00:57:47.546
I jas ti go pozeluvam istoto.

00:57:52.513 --> 00:57:58.669
Toj e star prijatel.
Imavme mnogu za sto da govorime.

00:57:59.320 --> 00:58:01.320
Se razbira.

00:58:02.520 --> 00:58:04.570
Togas?

00:58:04.775 --> 00:58:11.165
Koj e Benito Kastelucio
i zosto ti donel cvece?

00:58:12.375 --> 00:58:16.364
Bese star i mnogu debel,

00:58:16.717 --> 00:58:19.593
a zdivot mu mirisase na cigari.

00:58:21.400 --> 00:58:23.517
Izvini, sto bev taka dobra.

00:58:24.273 --> 00:58:26.273
Si zaminuva sabajle.

00:58:36.920 --> 00:58:40.510
Cudesno, g-n Kauc. Odlicno.

00:58:40.716 --> 00:58:42.716
Se e kako sto zboruvavme.

00:58:46.740 --> 00:58:52.570
Sosema li ste siguren,
deka go sakate ova, gospodaru Ŕsli?

00:58:54.095 --> 00:58:56.105
Sosema siguren?

00:58:56.517 --> 00:58:59.051
Ima i drugo, g-n Kauc,
ako nemate protiv?

00:59:09.253 --> 00:59:13.113
Site li, gospodaru Ŕsli?
- Site, g-n Kauc.

00:59:36.150 --> 00:59:38.150
Taa znae li nesto za toa?

00:59:39.060 --> 00:59:41.060
Ne.

00:59:41.729 --> 00:59:45.139
I si sosema resen na ovoj poteg?
- Sosema.

00:59:56.310 --> 00:59:59.440
Sosema si zaslepen
od bratucetka ti, neli?

01:00:00.084 --> 01:00:02.514
Go pravam toa, sto mislam deka e pravilno.

01:00:02.961 --> 01:00:06.971
Svacas, deka moze da zagubis se?
- Spremen sum da go prevzemam toj rizik.

01:00:07.171 --> 01:00:10.383
Osven, ako taa se omazi. po tret pat.
- Ěalku e verojatno.

01:00:10.539 --> 01:00:14.869
Ne smetam, deka si mislel da i predlozis?
- Zosto?

01:00:24.227 --> 01:00:26.242
Ěnogu dobro.

01:00:29.557 --> 01:00:31.557
Neka...

01:00:40.920 --> 01:00:42.920
Eve tuka.

01:00:47.427 --> 01:00:49.427
Blagodaram.

01:01:17.495 --> 01:01:19.495
Gotovo.

01:01:22.085 --> 01:01:24.085
Blagodaram.

01:01:34.762 --> 01:01:38.536
Blagodaram za tvojata ljubov prema
mene i Ŕmbrouz.

01:01:39.776 --> 01:01:42.236
I tvojata zakrilata niz godinite.

01:01:43.485 --> 01:01:47.375
Zakrila, koja zavrsuva utre.
- Vecer, vsusnost.

01:01:50.947 --> 01:01:56.477
Cestit rodenden, Filip,
vecer na polnoc.

01:02:03.966 --> 01:02:06.400
Ne mislamk deka sakas da ja vidis Luiz?

01:02:07.889 --> 01:02:10.463
Tuka li e?
- Da.

01:02:15.383 --> 01:02:17.383
Ěislam deka treba...
- Ne.

01:02:19.969 --> 01:02:23.399
Zosto ne naminete utre? Dvajcata?

01:02:24.127 --> 01:02:26.167
Da se napiete za moe zdravje?

01:02:35.014 --> 01:02:37.014
Dobro utro, Źosua!

01:02:44.497 --> 01:02:46.497
Gospodaru Ŕsli!

01:02:47.520 --> 01:02:49.616
Gospodaru Ŕsli!

01:02:50.662 --> 01:02:53.296
Dobro sum!

01:02:58.239 --> 01:03:01.112
Imate sreca sto stenata
ne se stovari vrz vas.

01:03:04.159 --> 01:03:06.229
Bev na nekolku milji.

01:03:07.891 --> 01:03:09.901
Blagodaram.

01:03:10.858 --> 01:03:13.214
Se e vo red.
- Ne ja sakate li?

01:03:15.254 --> 01:03:18.284
Se odminale nesreca, neli?
- Stenata po patot.

01:03:18.952 --> 01:03:22.382
Gorn Őed. Patot propadna
vo moreto pod mene.

01:03:23.238 --> 01:03:25.328
Da, polnata mesecina, plimata.

01:03:26.076 --> 01:03:28.193
Propadna sosema, potoa.

01:03:41.574 --> 01:03:43.574
Rejcel.

01:03:47.786 --> 01:03:50.796
Rejcel.
- Sto ima?

01:03:50.948 --> 01:03:53.047
Imam nesto za tebe.

01:03:53.464 --> 01:03:55.464
Spijam.

01:04:07.307 --> 01:04:10.477
Filip. Sto pravis?

01:04:11.320 --> 01:04:13.370
Ťe si go skrsi vratot.

01:04:16.017 --> 01:04:18.017
Ťe si go skrsis vratot.

01:04:33.680 --> 01:04:36.356
Se e vo red. Óspeav.

01:04:46.063 --> 01:04:49.774
Ěalku sum stara za Łulija,
ne mislis li?

01:04:55.105 --> 01:04:57.105
Toa...

01:04:57.710 --> 01:04:59.747
Sakam da go procitas pismoto.

01:05:01.761 --> 01:05:03.761
Toa...

01:05:05.320 --> 01:05:07.320
Sakam sega da gi imas.

01:05:10.511 --> 01:05:14.061
Sosema si poludel.
- Vidi, imam 25.

01:05:14.261 --> 01:05:16.293
Ěozam da pravam, sto ce posakam.

01:05:28.066 --> 01:05:30.066
Stavi go ova.

01:05:51.160 --> 01:05:53.160
Sakam samo edno,

01:05:55.028 --> 01:05:57.065
no nema da molam za nego.

01:05:58.595 --> 01:06:01.847
Zosto?
- Zatoa sto ce mi se priblizis.

01:06:02.880 --> 01:06:04.880
Kazi mi.

01:06:08.110 --> 01:06:10.186
Znam...

01:06:14.120 --> 01:06:18.250
Znam sto mi nedostasuva.

01:06:21.531 --> 01:06:23.966
Znaes?
- Da.

01:06:26.031 --> 01:06:30.131
Siguren li si?
- Da.

01:06:48.709 --> 01:06:50.709
Cestit rodenden.

01:08:35.025 --> 01:08:37.755
Źon!
- Ser?

01:08:38.250 --> 01:08:40.860
Sakam kosnica za piknik.
- Da, ser.

01:08:41.056 --> 01:08:44.006
Piknik za dvajca so sise vino.
- Odlicno, ser.

01:08:44.407 --> 01:08:46.407
Vilington!

01:08:46.640 --> 01:08:48.640
Vilington!

01:08:50.171 --> 01:08:52.201
Kade e?
- Sto, ser?

01:08:52.353 --> 01:08:57.103
Kocijata.
- Ne znaete li, gospodarkata ja zede.

01:08:57.686 --> 01:09:01.816
Kade otidoa?
- Nemam pretstava, vo grad?

01:09:03.403 --> 01:09:06.293
Denot e cudesen za vasiot rodenden,
gospodaru Ŕsli.

01:09:06.460 --> 01:09:10.060
Da. Prekrasen den.

01:09:52.365 --> 01:09:54.365
Kade bese?

01:09:56.323 --> 01:09:58.554
Cekav celo utro.

01:10:00.040 --> 01:10:03.030
Sakas li malku?
- Ne, blagodaram.

01:10:03.230 --> 01:10:07.050
Kade bese?
- Bev vo Pelin da go vidam tvojot kum.

01:10:07.250 --> 01:10:09.282
Za sto?

01:10:09.482 --> 01:10:12.730
Formulacijata na tvojot dokument
bese malku nejasna

01:10:13.224 --> 01:10:16.379
i sakav da bidam sosema sigurna,
deka znam sto oznacuva.

01:10:16.986 --> 01:10:18.986
Sega jasno li e?

01:10:21.549 --> 01:10:23.549
Sosema.

01:10:27.112 --> 01:10:29.112
Kreni go velot.

01:10:44.419 --> 01:10:48.029
Znam, deka kum ti ne me odobruva,
no bese mnogu fin.

01:10:48.294 --> 01:10:50.724
Duri planiravme
da se sretneme vo London.

01:10:51.524 --> 01:10:54.174
Nemas namera da odis tamu, neli?

01:10:54.370 --> 01:10:56.470
Zosto ne?

01:11:01.403 --> 01:11:03.403
Kolku e ubavo.

01:11:06.441 --> 01:11:08.456
Sedni za moment.
- Ne sum umorna.

01:11:10.986 --> 01:11:13.976
Samo za moment.
- Sedev vo kocijata so casovi.

01:11:14.162 --> 01:11:19.652
Kako i jas sedev kako idiot
na vratata da te cekam da se vratis.

01:11:19.867 --> 01:11:21.867
Gotovo.

01:11:30.973 --> 01:11:32.973
Toa bese mojot plan,

01:11:35.301 --> 01:11:37.301
koj sto ti go rasipa,

01:11:41.116 --> 01:11:43.966
rucajci so zdodevniot star Kendal.

01:11:44.198 --> 01:11:46.613
Povece mislev deka ce e.

01:12:35.981 --> 01:12:37.981
Da stanam.

01:12:45.669 --> 01:12:49.069
Eve.
- Blagodaram.

01:12:51.817 --> 01:12:54.167
Ŕko znaev deka ce se zbogatam,

01:12:54.622 --> 01:12:57.062
ce ti dadev golema perla.

01:12:59.196 --> 01:13:01.196
Toa e cudesno. Blagodaram.

01:13:09.561 --> 01:13:11.561
Ťe trgneme li?

01:13:34.227 --> 01:13:37.057
Pozdravi od gospodarkata.
- Sto e toa?

01:13:38.749 --> 01:13:40.749
Supa od granki.

01:13:42.040 --> 01:13:44.714
Specijalno svarena za rodendenot

01:13:46.000 --> 01:13:48.000
Rece deka treba da ja ispiete.

01:13:57.836 --> 01:14:01.086
Potoa prodolzi da tancuva
okolu kucata,

01:14:01.286 --> 01:14:03.299
nagore i nadolu po skalite.

01:14:03.455 --> 01:14:07.085
Navistina, bese najcudniot trik,
koj sto sum go videl.

01:14:22.833 --> 01:14:25.583
Filip.
- Filip?

01:14:26.695 --> 01:14:29.195
Filip.
- Za tebe.

01:14:30.663 --> 01:14:35.333
Dolg zivot i sreca.

01:14:35.533 --> 01:14:37.546
Za Filip.
- Za tebe.

01:14:39.220 --> 01:14:43.590
I jas imam da nazdravam vecerva.

01:14:45.440 --> 01:14:48.130
Od ova utro sum

01:14:50.735 --> 01:14:52.735
najsrecniot od site mazi.

01:14:54.008 --> 01:14:59.018
Sakam ti, mojot kum i ti,

01:15:00.027 --> 01:15:03.627
mila Luiz, da piete za mojata sreca.

01:15:04.943 --> 01:15:09.162
Pricinata za ovaa sreca,

01:15:13.101 --> 01:15:15.311
e zenata, koja ce mi bide sopruga.

01:15:25.903 --> 01:15:27.903
Rejcel.

01:15:33.320 --> 01:15:35.320
Ěila moja.

01:15:37.296 --> 01:15:39.296
Da ne si poludel?

01:15:40.080 --> 01:15:42.080
Se razbira, deka ne.

01:15:42.680 --> 01:15:44.680
Ve molam.

01:15:45.080 --> 01:15:48.450
Vozbudata od rodendenot go obzela

01:15:48.767 --> 01:15:51.601
i treba da se odmorime vo sosednata soba.

01:16:09.951 --> 01:16:12.341
Go znam sramot vo svojot zivot.

01:16:13.320 --> 01:16:15.320
Ózasniot sram.

01:16:16.297 --> 01:16:18.528
No toa e najlosoto.

01:16:26.963 --> 01:16:29.873
Ne bese zasramena sinoca,
nitu pak utrinava.

01:16:30.111 --> 01:16:32.111
Zasramena od sto?

01:16:33.787 --> 01:16:35.787
Zosto da se sramam od toa?

01:16:36.640 --> 01:16:40.490
Ěe prasa sto mi nedostasuva,

01:16:40.690 --> 01:16:43.472
a jas ti rekov deka edinstvenoto,
sto mi nedostasuva...

01:16:43.920 --> 01:16:46.510
Boze.
- Bese...

01:16:49.440 --> 01:16:51.440
Bese...

01:16:54.200 --> 01:16:56.200
Ti.

01:16:59.650 --> 01:17:01.780
Ne ti li se dopadna?
- Ne li?

01:17:02.153 --> 01:17:05.523
Sakav da ti se dopadne, da ti blagodaram.

01:17:05.723 --> 01:17:09.189
Za sto?
- Za sto li? Za se.

01:17:10.102 --> 01:17:13.512
Deka bese tolku fin so mene,
za nakitot.

01:17:13.954 --> 01:17:18.104
Sto, ti...
Ěislese, deka si me kupil?

01:17:18.520 --> 01:17:20.550
Cekaj, te molam.

01:17:20.779 --> 01:17:23.089
Bakni me, te molam.
- Pusti mi ja rakata.

01:17:23.419 --> 01:17:25.849
Bakni me, te molam.
- Pupsti mi ja rakata.

01:17:26.049 --> 01:17:28.146
Bakni me.
- Pusti me.

01:18:06.070 --> 01:18:08.944
Se grizev za tebe odamna.

01:18:12.166 --> 01:18:14.166
Od pred Bozik.

01:18:21.080 --> 01:18:23.080
Ne znaes nisto za nea.

01:18:24.480 --> 01:18:26.880
Ili ti si toj, koj sto ne znae.

01:18:38.920 --> 01:18:40.920
Nema smisol.

01:18:42.136 --> 01:18:45.566
Te sakam i ti mene,
no ako prodolzime da govorime

01:18:45.749 --> 01:18:47.749
ce svrsime mrazejci se eden so drug.

01:18:55.480 --> 01:18:57.770
Ła sakas li tolku mnogu?

01:18:57.920 --> 01:19:01.690
Ne znam kolku glupav
treba da ti izgledam.

01:19:01.840 --> 01:19:03.957
Ła zamoliv da se omazi za mene.

01:19:06.800 --> 01:19:09.952
Ťe prodolzam da ja prasuvam.

01:19:15.120 --> 01:19:17.810
Koga tocno ja prasa?

01:19:18.800 --> 01:19:23.050
Na mojot rodenden, vcera.

01:19:26.581 --> 01:19:28.641
Taa sto rece?

01:19:29.685 --> 01:19:31.725
Ěislev deka ce kaze "Da."

01:19:33.994 --> 01:19:36.064
Nomala predvid "Ne."

01:19:36.264 --> 01:19:39.040
Toa bese, pred ili posle otkako
go procita dokumentot?

01:19:39.232 --> 01:19:41.242
Porano. Go procita sabajleto.

01:19:41.408 --> 01:19:45.858
Ne gubese vreme da dojde kaj nas.
- Rece deka ne go razbira potpolno.

01:19:46.058 --> 01:19:48.898
Go razbra dosta dobro,
koga si zamina.

01:19:49.104 --> 01:19:53.374
Stoevme na skalite na sonce,
cekajci ja nejzinaat kocija

01:19:53.601 --> 01:19:55.651
a tatko mi i rece:

01:19:55.851 --> 01:19:58.853
"Klauzulata za brak moze
malku da ti otezne."

01:19:59.167 --> 01:20:02.739
Treba da ostanes vdovica,
ako sakas da si go socuvas bogatstvoto."

01:20:04.659 --> 01:20:06.689
Taa sto rece?

01:20:06.885 --> 01:20:10.855
Se nasmevna, si gi stavi rakavicite

01:20:11.589 --> 01:20:14.123
i rece: "Toa mi odgovara mnogu dobro."

01:20:19.984 --> 01:20:22.494
Taa klauzula e, za da
go socuva imotot.

01:20:23.557 --> 01:20:27.227
Ŕko mi bese sopruga,
nemase da se primeni.

01:20:27.462 --> 01:20:30.032
Ne, gresis.

01:20:30.328 --> 01:20:36.398
Ŕko se omazi za tebe ili drug,
kucata i se se vraca kaj tebe.

01:20:36.951 --> 01:20:41.821
Łas ce spodelam se so nea,
sekoe peni i taa go znae.

01:20:42.388 --> 01:20:45.859
Soprugata ne moze da ispraca
pari nadvor od zemjata.

01:20:46.838 --> 01:20:51.088
Ťe treba da zivee tuka
vo Ŕnglija so svojot soprug.

01:21:06.411 --> 01:21:09.071
Balama.

01:21:14.912 --> 01:21:17.002
Zdravo, Filip.

01:21:17.202 --> 01:21:21.019
Ła pokaniv Ěeri Paskoa da ostane
vo kucata so mene, kako moja pridruznicka.

01:21:21.632 --> 01:21:26.422
Se nadevam, deka odobruvas.
- Igras li? Toa e kribidz.

01:21:27.734 --> 01:21:30.304
Ěoze li da govoram so tebe?
- Da.

01:21:30.553 --> 01:21:33.203
Ěozam da te naucma, ako sakas?
- Nasamo.

01:21:33.414 --> 01:21:36.490
Se, sto sakas da kazes,
moze da e pred Ěeri.

01:21:42.490 --> 01:21:45.080
Ne sakam da se preckam.
Ťe odam vo svojata soba.

01:21:45.280 --> 01:21:48.470
Ostavi ja vratata otvorena,
za da me cues, ako mi potrebas.

01:21:48.717 --> 01:21:50.717
Se razbira, g-do Ŕsli.

01:21:54.805 --> 01:21:57.035
Ne go pravi toa.
- Koe?

01:21:57.223 --> 01:21:59.260
Ne ja zatvoraj vratata.

01:22:08.545 --> 01:22:10.715
Posle sinoca ne mozam da bidam sama so tebe.

01:22:12.187 --> 01:22:14.187
Te molam, ne go pravi toa.

01:22:14.355 --> 01:22:16.355
Ne se cuvstvuvam bezbedna so tebe.

01:22:18.051 --> 01:22:20.051
Te prekolnuvam.

01:23:02.182 --> 01:23:04.252
<i>Boze, ako bev na tvoe mesto,</i>

01:23:04.452 --> 01:23:06.738
<i>ce go naterav d-r Smol
da go pogledne toa.</i>

01:23:32.239 --> 01:23:34.239
Slaba Bogu.

01:23:35.241 --> 01:23:37.241
Ti se vrati.

01:23:40.918 --> 01:23:42.918
Eve.

01:23:46.305 --> 01:23:48.501
Rejcel...
- Ne govori.

01:23:49.883 --> 01:23:51.883
Eve.

01:23:59.618 --> 01:24:01.618
Kolku vreme bev vo besoznanie?

01:24:03.386 --> 01:24:05.386
Pet dena.

01:24:07.213 --> 01:24:09.213
Ŕ devojceto Paskoa?

01:24:10.901 --> 01:24:12.901
Si zamina.

01:24:13.959 --> 01:24:15.959
Ne mrdajte.

01:24:19.623 --> 01:24:22.673
Drago mi e da vidam deka Vilington
go otsece zlatniot dozdec.

01:24:22.996 --> 01:24:25.086
Sto e toa?

01:24:25.286 --> 01:24:27.322
Ŕko go oodgrize konj, ce go ubie.

01:24:27.554 --> 01:24:30.464
Imas eden vo Italija.

01:24:31.153 --> 01:24:33.153
Taka li?

01:24:33.607 --> 01:24:36.957
Kraj fontanata vo saksija. Pametis li?
- Taka li?

01:24:38.742 --> 01:24:41.111
Ne moze da se ocekuva
se da pametam.

01:25:00.250 --> 01:25:02.250
Eve.

01:25:14.121 --> 01:25:16.121
Pij.

01:25:59.455 --> 01:26:01.486
Kade odis?

01:26:05.720 --> 01:26:09.450
Kade?
Se grzis deka ce gi izmoram konjite?

01:26:11.735 --> 01:26:13.735
Ne.

01:26:19.264 --> 01:26:21.264
Se grizam deka ce si zamines.

01:26:28.464 --> 01:26:30.464
Ěe napustas li?

01:26:35.973 --> 01:26:38.283
Trebase da me ostavis da umram.
- Nemoj.

01:26:40.468 --> 01:26:42.618
Brzo nema da izgleda tolku loso.

01:26:43.485 --> 01:26:45.485
Ěestoto ti e tuka.

01:26:46.892 --> 01:26:52.182
Za kratko pak ce bides silen i se,
ce bide kako sto bese, pred da dojdam.

01:26:53.071 --> 01:26:55.427
Ti si vo pocetokot na se.

01:26:57.998 --> 01:26:59.998
Ěomcence.

01:27:02.102 --> 01:27:04.298
Kako mozam da ziveam so momce?

01:27:06.592 --> 01:27:08.592
Kolku i da sarmantno.

01:27:10.800 --> 01:27:12.800
Prekrasno milenice,

01:27:13.200 --> 01:27:18.390
koe skita naokolu, bedno
so mokar nos, koe si ja bara majka si.

01:27:24.108 --> 01:27:26.108
Pij.

01:27:26.595 --> 01:27:28.595
Pij.

01:27:46.480 --> 01:27:51.390
<i>"Gi ispiva site pari kako voda,
alcna za se."</i>

01:27:52.432 --> 01:27:54.808
<i>No e umna i itra.</i>

01:27:56.676 --> 01:27:59.926
<i>Toa e bolest. Ne moze da se vozdrzi.</i>

01:28:00.196 --> 01:28:02.506
<i>Ťe go zeme sekoe peni.</i>

01:28:02.701 --> 01:28:07.751
<i>Ťe me unisti. Ťe ne unisti nas, se."</i>

01:28:12.296 --> 01:28:14.296
Sto e toa?

01:28:15.720 --> 01:28:17.720
Nisto.

01:28:18.806 --> 01:28:20.806
Sto bese?

01:28:21.232 --> 01:28:23.232
Nisto.

01:29:45.996 --> 01:29:47.996
Toj zosto e tuka?

01:29:48.903 --> 01:29:51.053
Zatoa sto go zamoliv.
- Zosto?

01:29:51.302 --> 01:29:54.472
Zosto ne? Ěi trebase sovet.

01:29:54.801 --> 01:29:57.660
Za sto?
- Ne e tvoja rabota.

01:30:02.197 --> 01:30:04.287
Kolku vreme me lazes?

01:30:05.000 --> 01:30:07.010
Go mrazis.

01:30:07.250 --> 01:30:10.540
Ŕko ti bev kazala, deka e tuka,
pak ce odvatese.

01:30:10.736 --> 01:30:13.866
Isprati go!

01:30:14.066 --> 01:30:16.076
Zosto da ne go dovedam tuka?

01:30:16.226 --> 01:30:19.626
Polude li?
- Ťe ostanes tuka kako moj zastitnik.

01:30:19.826 --> 01:30:22.513
Ťe ostanes vo mojata spalna.
- Ne bi se osmelila.

01:30:22.717 --> 01:30:26.607
Zosto ne?
Zosto da nemam svoj zivot

01:30:26.839 --> 01:30:29.649
da go ziveam i pravam sto sakam?

01:30:30.444 --> 01:30:34.374
Ovaa kuca e moja i pokraj se, neli?

01:30:34.609 --> 01:30:36.660
Ne e li moja?
- Boze!

01:30:37.911 --> 01:30:41.681
Ěavni se od mene!
Stoj podaleku od mene!

01:30:42.205 --> 01:30:45.203
Ili ce gi povikam slugite.
Stoj podaleku!

01:30:46.691 --> 01:30:50.461
Sakas li da se posramis pred niv?

01:31:06.151 --> 01:31:08.151
Ŕjde.

01:31:09.169 --> 01:31:11.169
Povikaj gi.

01:31:13.311 --> 01:31:15.341
Site.

01:31:15.560 --> 01:31:17.560
Ŕjde.

01:31:18.686 --> 01:31:21.221
Kazi im sto se sluci tuka medu nas.

01:31:22.945 --> 01:31:24.945
Se.

01:31:28.730 --> 01:31:31.220
Stavi kraj na toa.

01:31:31.980 --> 01:31:33.980
Premnogusum umoren.

01:31:34.390 --> 01:31:36.390
Izmoren sum da se boram.

01:31:47.123 --> 01:31:49.240
Ne mozam da go napravam pak.

01:31:54.017 --> 01:31:56.017
Ne mozam.

01:31:59.492 --> 01:32:02.212
Se.

01:32:04.288 --> 01:32:07.584
Duri i racete na mojot vrat.

01:32:10.225 --> 01:32:12.225
Ne mozam.

01:32:14.266 --> 01:32:17.882
Ne mozam da napravma odnovo se.

01:32:41.429 --> 01:32:45.399
Bev mnogu blagodaren za paltoto
na g-n Ŕmbrouz, g-n Ŕsli.

01:32:45.844 --> 01:32:50.587
Ne sum go staval do pred vcera.
Premnogu e ubavo za mene.

01:32:51.060 --> 01:32:53.810
Bev mnogu blagodaren, g-n Ŕsli,
mnogu blagodaren.

01:32:54.010 --> 01:32:58.422
Ła staviv rakata vo dzebot
i tamu bese ova, gospodaru Ŕsli.

01:32:59.111 --> 01:33:01.111
Seuste e zapecateno.

01:33:04.241 --> 01:33:07.771
<i>"Ti si edinstveniot covek vo svetot,
komu mozam da mu veruvam.</i>

01:33:09.018 --> 01:33:11.952
<i>Ostavi se. Izlezi kaj mene.</i>

01:33:12.890 --> 01:33:14.890
<i>Samo dojdi sto pobrzo.</i>

01:33:16.944 --> 01:33:18.944
<i>Se palsam za svojot zivot.</i>

01:33:20.191 --> 01:33:23.043
<i>Glavobolkite, bolesta, treskata,</i>

01:33:24.303 --> 01:33:26.303
<i>nenadejno razbrav.</i>

01:33:28.284 --> 01:33:32.437
<i>Gorclivite otrovi me truea.</i>

01:33:36.058 --> 01:33:38.457
<i>Za celo vreme me truela."</i>

01:33:46.570 --> 01:33:48.570
Bev glupak.

01:34:31.086 --> 01:34:35.896
Vo Firenca varev caj vo salonot

01:34:36.079 --> 01:34:38.329
i go ostavav za kratko.

01:34:38.941 --> 01:34:41.931
Potoa izleguvavme
za malku vo dvorot,

01:34:42.169 --> 01:34:44.459
ako ne bese mnogu zesko i sedevme.

01:34:44.676 --> 01:34:49.306
Ła pustav fontanata i go pievme cajot.

01:34:50.513 --> 01:34:52.982
Ŕmbrouz stoese tamu so casovi.

01:34:56.380 --> 01:34:59.410
Poveli. Ne, ovaa. Taa e za Filip.

01:34:59.733 --> 01:35:02.133
Blagodaram.
- Poveli.

01:35:02.947 --> 01:35:04.997
Ne, blagodaram.

01:35:05.197 --> 01:35:08.257
Specijalen e. Go napraviv posilen.

01:35:08.607 --> 01:35:10.607
Ispij go mesto mene.

01:35:12.990 --> 01:35:14.990
Sto mislis?

01:35:22.387 --> 01:35:24.557
Ěnogu e interesen.

01:35:27.410 --> 01:35:29.942
Ťe mi treba malku vreme
da se vljubam vo nego.

01:35:38.270 --> 01:35:40.421
Koj ce dojde da java so mene?

01:35:41.270 --> 01:35:43.680
Ěoze da ja zemem kocijata,
ako pretpocitate.

01:35:44.664 --> 01:35:46.694
Ti odi.

01:35:46.860 --> 01:35:49.830
So Luiz imame da nesto da zboruvame.

01:35:50.054 --> 01:35:54.084
Vie imate?
Kakva zaguba na den kako ovoj.

01:36:00.788 --> 01:36:02.788
Dobro, ce odam sama.

01:36:08.821 --> 01:36:11.853
Nema da se zabavam.
Dovrsete si go cajot.

01:36:17.867 --> 01:36:23.117
Kade odis?
- Ne znam. Barton Őil, mozebi.

01:36:23.716 --> 01:36:27.006
Ili vo gorata.
Dali zumbulite se uste tamu?

01:36:27.436 --> 01:36:29.506
Odavma gi nema, se plasam.

01:36:31.717 --> 01:36:35.667
Ěoze da go probas patot kraj stenite.
- Da, dobra ideja.

01:36:35.985 --> 01:36:39.101
Ima tulencinja
vo ova vreme od godinata.

01:36:41.443 --> 01:36:43.460
Izgledas podobro.

01:36:44.824 --> 01:36:49.124
Ŕ ti - ubava.

01:36:55.280 --> 01:36:57.280
Ćalam.

01:37:08.030 --> 01:37:10.080
Sto baras?

01:37:10.481 --> 01:37:13.040
Seminja od zlaten dozdec, pisma.
Ne znam.

01:37:17.219 --> 01:37:19.869
Go otrula Ŕmbrouz, me true i mene.
Ne gledas li?

01:37:23.697 --> 01:37:25.707
Kauc, advokatot.

01:37:27.136 --> 01:37:29.406
<i>"Vi blagodarime za vracanjeto
na nakitot,</i>

01:37:30.004 --> 01:37:32.794
<i>sto spored vasite instrukcii
ce ostane so nas,</i>

01:37:33.076 --> 01:37:36.346
<i>dodeka vasiot naslednik, Filip Ŕsli
go prevzeme vladeenjeto nad niv."</i>

01:37:39.097 --> 01:37:41.097
Gi vratila.

01:37:44.146 --> 01:37:47.536
Nakitot, go vratila.
- Prodolzi da baras.

01:37:48.144 --> 01:37:50.594
Filip, ne znam sto barame.

01:37:50.746 --> 01:37:53.486
Ne treba li...
- Prodolzi da baras, te molam!

01:38:01.861 --> 01:38:04.381
Eve, na italijanski e.
Treba da e od Renaldi.

01:38:05.945 --> 01:38:09.215
Toj li e?
- Potpisano e Enriko.

01:38:09.415 --> 01:38:11.574
Toa e toj. Prevedi go, te molam.

01:38:11.769 --> 01:38:14.139
<i>"Draga Rejcel, razmisli,</i>

01:38:14.356 --> 01:38:17.686
<i>ako ne mozes da dojdes
i da go ostavis momceto,</i>

01:38:18.809 --> 01:38:20.839
<i>dovedi go so tebe.</i>

01:38:21.548 --> 01:38:24.258
<i>Óste mislamk deka ne e dobra ideja,</i>

01:38:25.703 --> 01:38:29.253
<i>no Italija i malku sonce,</i>

01:38:29.941 --> 01:38:32.341
<i>moze da mu vlijae dobro."</i>

01:38:39.377 --> 01:38:41.427
Toa li e?

01:38:42.748 --> 01:38:45.208
Filip, bea napraveni proucuvanja.
Tatko mi...

01:38:46.230 --> 01:38:48.280
Kakvi proucuvanja?

01:38:48.480 --> 01:38:50.724
Od emocionalna gledna tocka,
izgleda...

01:38:52.132 --> 01:38:56.451
Deka Enriko Renaldi, e povece grk,
otkolku italijanec.

01:39:00.108 --> 01:39:02.108
Ěu se dopadaat momcinja, Filip.

01:39:14.310 --> 01:39:16.310
Velington!

01:39:17.732 --> 01:39:20.003
Ťe go donesa msedloto!
- Po davolite sedloto!

01:40:27.430 --> 01:40:29.430
<i>Koj e vinoven?</i>

01:40:34.051 --> 01:40:36.051
<i>Bev sirak.</i>

01:40:37.037 --> 01:40:39.037
<i>Ŕmbrouz me zede.</i>

01:40:41.175 --> 01:40:46.075
<i>Ěi bese bratuced,
no go sakav kako tatko.</i>

01:40:48.100 --> 01:40:50.100
<i>Sega, jas sum tatko.</i>

01:40:53.652 --> 01:40:55.652
<i>Na sto mozam da gi naucam?</i>

01:40:56.510 --> 01:40:58.510
<i>Sto da im kazam?</i>

01:41:00.882 --> 01:41:02.882
<i>Glavobolkite me zaslepuvaat.</i>

01:41:05.282 --> 01:41:07.282
<i>Taa li bese?</i>

01:41:08.487 --> 01:41:10.487
<i>Taa li go napravi?</i>

01:41:11.281 --> 01:41:13.281
<i>Ne e li taa?</i>

01:41:25.031 --> 01:41:27.062
<i>Rejcel, mojata tortura.</i>

01:41:30.062 --> 01:41:34.062
